    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You physically change your body, making it younger by 1 or 2 age categories, changing your appearance and replacing your age penalties with those of the new age category. This may include changing your size.<br><br>This technique lasts until 1d4+1 rounds after your Chakra Pool falls below 10%, or it can be dismissed as any dismissible technique can.</p>\n\n\n\n",
